    "description": {
      "value": "<p>Your <em>warmask</em> sharpens your connection to the source of your mask's power. During your daily preparations, choose @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.spells-srd.Item.4koZzrnMXhhosn0D]{Fear}, @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.spells-srd.Item.R8bqnYiThB6MYTxD]{Phantom Pain}, or @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.spells-srd.Item.Gb7SeieEvd0pL2Eh]{Sure Strike}.</p>\n<p>Until your next daily preparations, you can cast this spell as a 1st-rank innate spell once per day; the spell's tradition is determined by the tradition tied to your <em>warmask</em>. You must be wearing your <em>warmask</em> to Cast the Spell.</p>",
